    \ingroup grp_commentable

    Default row class is ZfBlank_Commentable.

    Besides all inherited table features, this table keeps information about
    comments related table. Relation between two tables is one-to-many
    (one item -- many comments). Comments table class is
    ZfBlank_DbTable_Comments or descendant.

    Reference physical schema is the same as for ZfBlank_DbTable_Items.
